y\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 920}, {\"ngram\": \"Tarling\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 929}, {\"ngram\": \"his competition\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 953}, {\"ngram\": \"his title\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 973}, {\"ngram\": \"the 30-kilometre course\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 1000}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year, Tarling's season is built around the 27th of July, the day of the men's Olympic time trial.\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1226, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tarling's season\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1151}, {\"ngram\": \"the 27th\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1176}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1184}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's Olympic time trial\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1225}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The National Championships were viewed as \\\"the last big hit\\\" before that goal, according to Ineos Grenadiers directeur sportif Ian Stannard, on a course not too dissimilar from the one in Paris, with a couple of testing but short ascents and technical sections.\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1488, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1319, \"end\": 1335, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos_Grenadiers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ineos Grenadiers\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos_Grenadiers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos_Grenadiers\"}, {\"begin\": 1354, \"end\": 1366, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ian_Stannard\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ian Stannard\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ian_Stannard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ian_Stannard\"}, {\"begin\": 1415, \"end\": 1420, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.367994988255212e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"