: 1679}, {\"ngram\": \"some final tweaks\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1715}, {\"ngram\": \"a new position\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1751}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think we are getting there.\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1799, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is a few things I need to sharpen up, but now it's slowly progressing,\\\" Tarling toldCyclingnewsafter the podium ceremony.\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1927, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few things\", \"from\": 1809, \"to\": 1821}, {\"ngram\": \"toldCyclingnewsafter\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1906}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium ceremony\", \"from\": 1907, \"to\": 1926}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was a new position, so it was quite a drastic change definitely from last year, but from the start of the season as well.\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 2054, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a new position\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 1951}, {\"ngram\": \"quite a drastic change\", \"from\": 1963, \"to\": 1985}, {\"ngram\": \"last year\", \"from\": 2002, \"to\": 2011}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 2022, \"to\": 2031}, {\"ngram\": \"the season\", \"from\": 2035, \"to\": 2045}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a bit tight in places, but it was good to get an all-out effort in the position.\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2140, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"places\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2081}, {\"ngram\": \"an all-out effort\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2123}, {\"ngram\": \"the position\", \"from\": 2127, \"to\": 2139}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will train a bit more in it, and hopefully, it'll all get sharper and tidier.\\\"\", \"from\": 2141, \"to\": 2221, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The latest race content, interviews, features, reviews and expert buying guides, direct to your inbox!\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2325, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The latest race content\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2246}, {\"ngram\": \"interviews\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2258}, {\"ngram\": \"features\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2268}, {\"ngram\": \"reviews\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2277}, {\"ngram\": \"expert buying guides\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2302}, {\"ngram\": \"your inbox\", \"from\": 2314, \"to\": 2324}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There wasn't much in the way of new tech being tested this week, with Tarling and his Ineos Grenadiers team-mates, Ethan Hayter and Conor Swift, all competing with a large single front chainring, which is quickly becoming the norm for these types of efforts.\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2585, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2413, \"end\": 2429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos_Grenadiers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ineos Grenadiers\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos_Grenadiers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ineos_Grenadiers\"}, {\"begin\": 2442, \"end\": 2454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethan_Hayter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ethan Hayter\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethan_Hayter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethan_Hayter\"}, {\"begin\": 2465, \"end\": 2470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\", \"score\": 0.9999999850197129, \"rank\": 1.4980230164952228e-08, \"text\": \"Swift\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2355}, {\"ngram\": \"new tech\", \"from\": 2359, \"to\": 2367}, {\"ngram\": \"Tarling\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2404}, {\"ngram\": \"a large single front chainring\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2521}, {\"ngram\": \"the norm\", \"from\": 2549, \"to\": 2557}, {\"ngram\": \"these types\", \"from\": 2562, \"to\": 2573}, {\"ngram\": \"efforts\", \"from\": 2577, \"to\": 2584}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stannard commented that the 20-year-old was \\\"training well, progressing well\\\" en route to Paris, adding that the course in north Yorkshire \\\"was a shorter time trial and it was quite technical with the climb and how steep it was, so he's done a great ride there and, yeah, onwards and upwards.\\\"\", \"from\": 2587, \"to\": 2880, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2677, \"end\": 2682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.367994988255212e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2710, \"end\": 2725, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Yorkshire\", \"score\": 0.9999994548940443, \"rank\": 5.451028346613987e-07, \"text\": \"north Yorkshire\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Yorkshire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Yorkshire\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Stannard\", \"from\": 2587, \"to\": 2595}, {\"ngram\": \"route\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 2673}, {\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 2696, \"to\": 2706}, {\"ngram\": \"a shorter time trial\", \"from\": 2731, \"to\": 2751}, {\"ngram\": \"the climb\", \"from\": 2784, \"to\": 2793}, {\"ngram\": \"a great ride\", \"from\": 2829, \"to\": 2841}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the road race on Sunday in Saltburn, Tarling will head to his first-ever altitude camp for his final Olympic preparations.\", \"from\": 2882, \"to\": 3010, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2915, \"end\": 2923, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saltburn-by-the-Sea\", \"score\": 0.9999995762142123, \"rank\": 4.2378587012330233e-07, \"text\": \"Saltburn\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saltburn-by-the-Sea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saltburn-by-the-S