3373, \"to\": 3398}, {\"ngram\": \"that sentiment\", \"from\": 3419, \"to\": 3433}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, things have not all been plain sailing in recent weeks.\", \"from\": 3435, \"to\": 3499, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 3444, \"to\": 3450}, {\"ngram\": \"plain sailing\", \"from\": 3469, \"to\": 3482}, {\"ngram\": \"recent weeks\", \"from\": 3486, \"to\": 3498}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tarling suffered a broken bone in his knee atParis Roubaixin April, which meant spending several weeks off the bike.\", \"from\": 3501, \"to\": 3617, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tarling\", \"from\": 3501, \"to\": 3508}, {\"ngram\": \"a broken bone\", \"from\": 3518, \"to\": 3531}, {\"ngram\": \"his knee\", \"from\": 3535, \"to\": 3543}, {\"ngram\": \"Roubaixin April\", \"from\": 3552, \"to\": 3567}, {\"ngram\": \"several weeks\", \"from\": 3590, \"to\": 3603}, {\"ngram\": \"the bike\", \"from\": 3608, \"to\": 3616}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He only returned to training on the 9th of May and to racing at theCrit\\u00e9rium du Dauphin\\u00e9a few weeks later.\", \"from\": 3618, \"to\": 3724, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 3638, \"to\": 3646}, {\"ngram\": \"the 9th\", \"from\": 3650, \"to\": 3657}, {\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 3661, \"to\": 3664}, {\"ngram\": \"theCrit\\u00e9rium\", \"from\": 3682, \"to\": 3694}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's put him back a little bit, you know, and it would have been nice for him to win that Dauphin\\u00e9 TT, he was keen for that.\", \"from\": 3726, \"to\": 3851, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3817, \"end\": 3825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dauphin\\u00e9\", \"score\": 0.9986989940517715, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dauphin\\u00e9\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dauphin\\u00e9\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dauphin\\u00e9\"}, {\"begin\": 3826, \"end\": 3828, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Man_TT\", \"score\": 0.9999988741066744, \"rank\": 1.1258947442671428e-06, \"text\": \"TT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Man_TT\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Man_TT\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But, you know, it's also slowed him down a little bit towards the Olympics and that's possibly a good thing,\\\" Stannard said, seeing the possible upside to Tarling's injury as decreasing the risk of overtraining before his big goal.\", \"from\": 3852, \"to\": 4083, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3914, \"to\": 3926}, {\"ngram\": \"a good thing\", \"from\": 3947, \"to\": 3959}, {\"ngram\": \"Stannard\", \"from\": 3962, \"to\": 3970}, {\"ngram\": \"the possible upside\", \"from\": 3984, \"to\": 4003}, {\"ngram\": \"Tarling's injury\", \"from\": 4007, \"to\": 4023}, {\"ngram\": \"the risk\", \"from\": 4038, \"to\": 4046}, {\"ngram\": \"his big goal\", \"from\": 4070, \"to\": 4082}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tarling said that he feels the effect of the lost training, but is trusting the team's process.\", \"from\": 4085, \"to\": 4180, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tarling\", \"from\": 4085, \"to\": 4092}, {\"ngram\": \"the effect\", \"from\": 4112, \"to\": 4122}, {\"ngram\": \"the lost training\", \"from\": 4126, \"to\": 4143}, {\"ngram\": \"the team's process\", \"from\": 4161, \"to\": 4179}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am not as sharp as I'd like to be, but I think in terms of fitness, I am alright.\", \"from\": 4182, \"to\": 4266, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 4235, \"to\": 4240}, {\"ngram\": \"fitness\", \"from\": 4244, \"to\": 4251}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We did a lot of non-riding stuff [during his injury recovery], so a bit of swimming, a bit of gym and stuff,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 4267, \"to\": 4385, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 4274, \"to\": 4279}, {\"ngram\": \"non-riding stuff\", \"from\": 4283, \"to\": 4299}, {\"ngram\": \"his injury recovery\", \"from\": 4308, \"to\": 4327}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 4342, \"to\": 4350}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 4352, \"to\": 4357}, {\"ngram\": \"gym\", \"from\": 4361, \"to\": 4364}, {\"ngram\": \"stuff\", \"from\": 4369, \"to\": 4374}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Fitness-wise, I am alright, but it's not as smooth as I'd like it to be.\", \"from\": 4386, \"to\": 4459, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am hacking away a bit, but it'll come.\\\"\", \"from\": 4460, \"to\": 4501, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After the Olympics, Tarling is hoping for a spot on Ineos Grenadiers' squad for La Vuelta a Espa\\u00f1a.\", \"from\": 4505, \"to\": 4604, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4585, \"end\": 4594, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vuelta_a_Espa\\u00f1a\", \"score\": 0.9999999981746441, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"La Vuelta\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\", \"Q15091377\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vuelta_a_Espa\\u00f1a\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vuelta_a_Espa\\u00f1a\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4511, \"to\": 4523}, {\"ngram\": \"Tarling\", \"from\": 4525, \"to\": 4532}, {\"ngram\": \"a spot\", \"from\": 4547, \"to\": 4553}, {\"ngram\": \"Ineos Grenadiers' squad\", \"from\": 4557, \"to\": 4580}, {\"ngram\": \"a Espa\\u00f1a\", \"from\": 4595, \"to\": 4603}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has one eye on the opening stage of this year's edition, a 12-kilometre solo effort from Lisbon to Oeiras, admitting \\\"I know there is a prologue but it's a bit of a grim one, so we will see.\\\"\", \"from\": 4605, \"to\": 4799, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4697, \"end\": 4703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisbon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.188283947483713e-17, \"text\": \"Lisbon\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org