rom\": 4844, \"to\": 4872}, {\"ngram\": \"a first Grand Tour\", \"from\": 4876, \"to\": 4894}, {\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 4899, \"to\": 4911}, {\"ngram\": \"attention\", \"from\": 4916, \"to\": 4925}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The parcours, however, is no less demanding than the other three-week races, with the climbs and heat of Spain often making the Vuelta seem like the toughest grand tour of the year.\", \"from\": 4988, \"to\": 5169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5093, \"end\": 5098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"score\": 0.7926626488826809, \"rank\": 0.2615673691372099, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The parcours\", \"from\": 4988, \"to\": 5000}, {\"ngram\": \"the other three-week races\", \"from\": 5037, \"to\": 5063}, {\"ngram\": \"the climbs\", \"from\": 5070, \"to\": 5080}, {\"ngram\": \"heat\", \"from\": 5085, \"to\": 5089}, {\"ngram\": \"the Vuelta\", \"from\": 5112, \"to\": 5122}, {\"ngram\": \"the toughest grand tour\", \"from\": 5133, \"to\": 5156}, {\"ngram\": \"the year\", \"from\": 5160, \"to\": 5168}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Tarling has already shown his climbing abilities this year.\", \"from\": 5171, \"to\": 5239, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tarling\", \"from\": 5180, \"to\": 5187}, {\"ngram\": \"his climbing abilities\", \"from\": 5206, \"to\": 5228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He put in a surprisingperformanceon the mountains of the Dauphin\\u00e9, supporting team leader Carlos Rodr\\u00edguez deep into the hardest stages of the race.\", \"from\": 5240, \"to\": 5388, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5297, \"end\": 5305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dauphin\\u00e9\", \"score\": 0.9986989940517715, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dauphin\\u00e9\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dauphin\\u00e9\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dauphin\\u00e9\"}, {\"begin\": 5330, \"end\": 5346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Rodr\\u00edguez_(darts_player)\", \"score\": 0.5023218714506964, \"rank\": 0.29629629629619897, \"text\": \"Carlos Rodr\\u00edguez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Rodr\\u00edguez_(darts_player)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Rodr\\u00edguez_(darts_player)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a surprisingperformanceon\", \"from\": 5250, \"to\": 5275}, {\"ngram\": \"the mountains\", \"from\": 5276, \"to\": 5289}, {\"ngram\": \"the hardest stages\", \"from\": 5357, \"to\": 5375}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 5379, \"to\": 5387}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's tempting to immediately draw parallels between Tarling and another winner of multiple British time-trial championships,Bradley Wiggins, who hauled his similarly large frame to a famous Tour de France win in 2012, and Britain's first.\", \"from\": 5390, \"to\": 5628, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5481, \"end\": 5488, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9975130822625969, \"rank\": 0.002275037708567339, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 5514, \"end\": 5529, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradley_Wiggins\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bradley Wiggins\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradley_Wiggins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradley_Wiggins\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"parallels\", \"from\": 5424, \"to\": 5433}, {\"ngram\": \"Tarling\", \"from\": 5442, \"to\": 5449}, {\"ngram\": \"another winner\", \"from\": 5454, \"to\": 5468}, {\"ngram\": \"his similarly large frame\", \"from\": 5542, \"to\": 5567}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When probed on whether we might one day see the Welshman make a similar transition from pure time triallist to overall classification contender, Tarling said \\\"I'd like to.\", \"from\": 5630, \"to\": 5801, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5678, \"end\": 5686, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales\", \"score\": 0.9999984223130636, \"rank\": 1.5776893900726758e-06, \"text\": \"Welshman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a similar transition\", \"from\": 5692, \"to\": 5712}, {\"ngram\": \"pure time triallist\", \"from\": 5718, \"to\": 5737}, {\"ngram\": \"overall classification contender\", \"from\": 5741, \"to\": 5773}, {\"ngram\": \"Tarling\", \"from\": 5775, \"to\": 5782}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have got to get skinny first, though.\\\"\", \"from\": 5802, \"to\": 5842, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To give some perspective, Tarling is reported to weigh around 20 kilograms more thanJonas Vingegaard(Visma-Lease a Bike), winner of the last two Tours de France.\", \"from\": 5844, \"to\": 6005, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5989, \"end\": 6004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tours de France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some perspective\", \"from\": 5852, \"to\": 5868}, {\"ngram\": \"Tarling\", \"from\": 5870, \"to\": 5877}, {\"ngram\": \"around 20 kilograms\", \"from\": 5899, \"to\": 5918}, {\"ngram\": \"thanJonas Vingegaard(Visma-Lease\", \"from\": 5924, \"to\": 5956}, {\"ngram\": \"a Bike\", \"from\": 5957, \"to\": 5963}, {\"ngram\": \"winner\", \"from\": 5966, \"to\": 5972}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I'd like to,\\\" he said, repeating himself, seeming to confirm that this is something he has thought a lo